Class VariantsTestReport

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
OmTestReport
public class VariantsTestReport
extends java.lang.Object
implements OmTestReport

This report analyses different variants of each question, and gives the number of students who was shown each variant, and their average scores. This gives some indication of whether the different variants are equally difficult. It relies on question authors adding "Variant = 123" somewhere in the questionline. Actually, the regular expression searched for is "[Vv]ariant\s*=\s*(\d+)".
